article.title: What is Corona Virus in 2 images
article.article:
The new coronavirus pandemic that began in Wuhan has no direct cure or publicly available vaccines yet. The virus is very contagious and can  live on a surface, like say, a door handle, on hard surfaces such as plastic and stainless steel for up to 72 hours and on cardboard for up to 24 hours.

Here is something that you can share with your loved ones:

There are limited resources, hospitals, doctors and care takers who can be of service. So do  your bit by taking the right precautions, understand the basics about the virus and your keep distance from others.

All the informations was tooked from different official sources
